{"tid":752523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[要不是外國疫苗]梁振英指無大陸市場大批港青失業　「風水佬唔呃得你好耐」","createTime":"2018-07-23T01:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T04:18:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55ccaad97661179432ac76d8621600d999b2f656","tid":752523,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要不是外國疫苗，你班支那人一早死撚晒啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00001/1532303707081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00001%2F1532303707081&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=570415b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00001%2F1532303707081&h=b637ece3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00001/1532303707081</a><br />\n<br />\n內地及香港政府都強調把握粵港澳大灣區發展機遇，全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英接受《星島日報》訪問時，再次推廣大灣區，稱若無大陸市場，「大批大批青年人失業」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在訪問中表示，年輕人是否到大灣區發展是個人選擇，「不是逼任何人去」，但形容這潮流浩浩蕩蕩。他又說，香港專業服務業過去十多年得以發展，修讀會計、建築等專業服務的大學生愈來愈多，稱：「如果冇咗大陸市場，佢哋點算？大批大批青年人失業，只不過十幾年前，風水佬唔呃得你好耐。」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英直言，不會人人到內地發展便順風順水，亦毋須每個香港人都去大灣區，「香港也要人為本地服務」。至於有人擔心香港會因此喪失自己特色及定位、「一國兩制」界線變得模糊，他重申任何規劃一定符合「一國兩制」、「港人治港」、「高度自治」及《基本法》規定，認為在不違反「一國兩制」下，有很多措施可「突破兩制之間的限制」，如科研資金「過河」。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英另建議日後香港私家車毋須申請中港牌，可經港珠澳大橋返回內地、外國公民持香港永久居民身分證，可免申請簽證進入大灣區，以及在一些大灣區需要的行業，港人於內地工作只須繳納香港稅率。他強調，港人要抱長遠心態看待大灣區發展，做好各方面連繫工作，不能守株待兔。"},{"pid":"b4ab3be2f640a0611e28117b77594351874633f9","tid":752523,"uid":26329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:47:47.000Z","msg":"上到去比人厄到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d9dc403d5ff50625eac5b3a178531616981098","tid":752523,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"5fa451887e915de11ca7ddc2ee99bcd734d96934","tid":752523,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"又搵水魚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8f6cb42328f948a9a1931885834dd1c3f62258","tid":752523,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"無外國勢力你唔會淨袋五千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64df8089efa6c42923125dd35a4b803bb50ff275","tid":752523,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"JR DEWI 打左疫苗未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9280da785a5d272b41ef20faccda720a65a525","tid":752523,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140604/large/04la7p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140604%2Flarge%2F04la7p9.jpg&h=624f9563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}